metadata.name: Squidnaut
metadata.description:
Squidnauts are trained to pilot and travel in spacecraft, work in space, and do activities related to squids from outer space. While space flight may now seem routine, every trip into space can be a walk between success and disaster. Therefore, most of a squidnaut's career is spent undergoing extensive training.

inspired by NASA's plan to send squid into space for research in 2021. As well as the theory of the octopus, an alien among us.
